---
title: Great Grape Pork Chops with Baby Broccoli and Sweet Potatoes
description: Grape salsa might just be a wonder condiment: it’s sophisticated enough for adult palates, yet features a fruit that’s pretty kid-friendly. We’re using it here to top pork chops, which always pair well with sweet flavors. Tender baby broccoli and sweet potatoes on the side round out this recipe, which has all the hallmarks of a weeknight dinner classic.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pan-seared-pork-chops-b3fac194.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/pan-seared-pork-chops-23a89e3b.pdf
